    "summary": "Lumin exposes a REST API at https://api.luminpdf.com/v1 authenticated by API key, HTTP Basic with API key, or OAuth 2.0 bearer token, plus a streamable-HTTP MCP server at https://mcp.luminpdf.com/mcp.",
